data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom home in NW Minot.  Enter into a 4 seasons enclosed porch/foyer large enough for a craft room, playroom or reading room.  Large living room and dining room with patio doors to the large, fenced backyard perfect for entertaining. Beautiful, updated kitchen with gorgeous hickory cabinets and high definition spacious countertops and a cabinet and countertop for a coffee bar. Solid oak wood surrounds the staircase that leads up to the 3 spacious bedroom and full bathroom.  Basement has plenty of space for a family room and a ¾ bathroom, extra storage and laundry area.  Single garage is insulated, heated and includes extra space with a workbench.  Extra parking on a concrete pad in the back alley.  There is a lot of old character in this charming home so take a look today.
